其他動物團體我諗一年三千隻都走唔甩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6xgD7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6xgD7B.jpg&h=8cbc10a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我講緊餵養嘅問題 愛佢就帶佢返屋企 帶唔到返屋企就搵人領養 搵唔到又唔想佢死就搵義工幫手 自私啲想留住佢繼續做流浪貓狗都捉去絕育先 要餵都唔好餵到飽晒肥肥白白 會令到佢哋失去求生能力 同會獵殺附近嘅野生動物嚟嬉戲"},{"pid":"f076e68837e6bf6475f733145c1c2a0c090b8fbe","tid":2382973,"uid":306922,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"498820ed5daa0ccf502b0e6c1c27272d7a2f3af3","tid":2382973,"uid":42374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8c17f92c7a4aef8f9f775124b21a138e4178ff5d","tid":2382973,"uid":306922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51a612fae344e30a72d0b18ba9b42bd0df9df85f","tid":2382973,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"啲流浪貓狗被人搵到會捉去絕育再放生..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"你又知你餵緊嗰隻係絕左育既？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"弱智都學人討論 基本常識都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咗絕育嘅耳仔會剪咗隻角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"你係咪肯定你既食物淨係會俾剪左角既貓狗食 係咪會一隻隻check"},{"pid":"7971fb1ffda244a6f2de3d199f9fa385d1ca1dd0","tid":2382973,"uid":245523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f076e68837e6bf6475f733145c1c2a0c090b8fbe","tid":2382973,"uid":306922,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"498820ed5daa0ccf502b0e6c1c27272d7a2f3af3","tid":2382973,"uid":42374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8c17f92c7a4aef8f9f775124b21a138e4178ff5d","tid":2382973,"uid":306922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"你又知你餵緊嗰隻係絕左育既？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"弱智都學人討論 基本常識都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咗絕育嘅耳仔會剪咗隻角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,